299
00:21:28,038 --> 00:21:32,986
Well, how about I walk you home?

300
00:21:34,159 --> 00:21:36,260
That's fine.

301
00:21:36,260 --> 00:21:38,160
I can manage.

302
00:22:12,451 --> 00:22:14,702
I knew this would happen.

303
00:22:15,335 --> 00:22:17,922
Come on. Let me walk you home.

304
00:22:22,630 --> 00:22:24,336
Thank you.

305
00:22:29,593 --> 00:22:31,406
What's wrong?

306
00:22:32,203 --> 00:22:34,084
You let out such a big sigh.

307
00:22:34,084 --> 00:22:37,121
Do you not want to talk with me that much?

308
00:22:37,121 --> 00:22:38,955
It's not that.

309
00:22:38,955 --> 00:22:41,786
I'm worried about the sports day.

310
00:22:41,786 --> 00:22:43,189
Why?

311
00:22:43,819 --> 00:22:49,798
Actually, I never want the competition to get this serious.

312
00:22:49,798 --> 00:22:52,796
But look what P'Aou and Yayah are doing.

313
00:22:55,340 --> 00:22:57,045
I get you.

314
00:22:57,045 --> 00:23:00,005
You just want it to be fun, right?

315
00:23:02,510 --> 00:23:07,594
Then let's help each other make it fun.

316
00:23:07,594 --> 00:23:12,861
Don't make the event very competitive. I will help you with that.

317
00:23:12,861 --> 00:23:15,614
Thank you for understanding.

318
00:23:27,200 --> 00:23:30,085
- Khru Prince, have you competed in a running race before?
- I haven't.

319
00:23:30,085 --> 00:23:31,803
Never? I'll guide you.

320
00:23:31,803 --> 00:23:33,144
There are four steps.

321
00:23:33,144 --> 00:23:35,991
First, get on your mark. Stand behind this line.

322
00:23:35,991 --> 00:23:39,307
