325
00:23:45,336 --> 00:23:46,578
Put it right here.

326
00:23:46,578 --> 00:23:49,490
Your left hand as well. That's right.

327
00:23:49,490 --> 00:23:52,850
In the third step, raise your body like this.

328
00:23:52,850 --> 00:23:55,782
Yes, that's right. And you can lower yourself a bit.

329
00:23:55,782 --> 00:23:57,862
Then look ahead.

330
00:23:57,862 --> 00:23:59,801
Do it like this.

331
00:24:02,423 --> 00:24:04,647
Khru Prince, what are you doing?

332
00:24:04,647 --> 00:24:08,407
