333
00:24:08,407 --> 00:24:11,174
- Can I help?
- Of course.

334
00:24:13,373 --> 00:24:16,230
- This team, too. Okay.
- One, two. One, two.

335
00:24:16,230 --> 00:24:19,310
- Try lifting.
- One, two.

336
00:24:20,400 --> 00:24:23,050
Go! Go!

337
00:24:26,503 --> 00:24:28,707
Am I doing it right?

338
00:24:28,707 --> 00:24:31,516
Yes. Keep making it into small pieces.

339
00:24:35,532 --> 00:24:37,137
Khru Prince.

340
00:24:38,848 --> 00:24:40,348
Here's some food.

341
00:24:40,348 --> 00:24:41,970
Thank you.

342
00:24:45,988 --> 00:24:48,622
There's grilled pork, too. Thank you.

343
00:24:58,937 --> 00:25:00,820
Did you pull a prank?

344
00:25:10,056 --> 00:25:11,311
Hey.

345
00:25:11,311 --> 00:25:15,031
The Village Headman asked me to bring you these sports jerseys.

346
00:25:16,358 --> 00:25:18,163
Are you home?

347
00:25:35,140 --> 00:25:38,811
Hey, what are you doing in the dark?

348
00:25:40,196 --> 00:25:41,802
Nature calls?

349
00:25:41,802 --> 00:25:45,327
Are you crazy? I'm searching for something.

350
00:25:45,327 --> 00:25:47,004
Searching?

351
00:25:47,004 --> 00:25:49,309
At night?

352
00:25:49,309 --> 00:25:52,609
Why didn't you look in the daytime?

353
00:25:52,609 --> 00:25:56,209
I know you're afraid of the dark.

354
00:25:56,209 --> 00:25:59,769
