- Hey!

356
00:26:02,509 --> 00:26:05,100
What the heck are you playing?

357
00:26:08,329 --> 00:26:09,601
What am I playing?

358
00:26:09,601 --> 00:26:14,709
I just wanted to see the reaction of someone so tight-lipped.

359
00:26:15,738 --> 00:26:18,934
So what are you looking for?

360
00:26:21,299 --> 00:26:24,521
The hair clip Viah gave to Sompor.

361
00:26:25,920 --> 00:26:28,998
The one Sompor threw away?

362
00:26:29,688 --> 00:26:33,951
Why? Do you want Viah to give it to her again?

363
00:26:33,951 --> 00:26:35,978
Yes.

364
00:26:35,978 --> 00:26:39,069
I've been looking since earlier.

365
00:26:39,069 --> 00:26:41,436
But I can't find it no matter what.

366
00:26:43,355 --> 00:26:45,969
Okay then. I will help.

367
00:26:45,969 --> 00:26:49,740
It's okay. I can do it myself.

368
00:26:49,740 --> 00:26:51,913
Hey.

369
00:26:51,913 --> 00:26:55,826
When people offer their help,

370
00:26:55,826 --> 00:26:58,432
you should learn to take it.

371
00:26:58,432 --> 00:27:00,569
There's no need to handle everything yourself.

372
00:27:00,569 --> 00:27:02,469
Here.

373
00:27:02,469 --> 00:27:04,498
I'll help you find it.

374
00:27:07,188 --> 00:27:12,880
Do you think those two will finally talk?

375
00:27:15,348 --> 00:27:18,797
You might not know this, but I can see it.

376
00:27:18,797 --> 00:27:21,801
Those two like each other very much.

377
00:27:22,723 --> 00:27:24,323
Yes?

378
00:27:24,323 --> 00:27:28,965
No wonder Sompor is so angry.

379
00:27:28,965 --> 00:27:30,946
Of course.

380
00:27:30,946 --> 00:27:33,709
And Viah is a tight-lipped one.

381
00:27:33,709 --> 00:27:35,908
He refuses to apologize.

382
00:27:35,908 --> 00:27:38,808
He refuses to say he likes her.

383
00:27:38,808 --> 00:27:41,483
He does things halfway.

384
00:27:41,483 --> 00:27:44,492
That's why Sompor gets angry.

385
00:27:44,492 --> 00:27:46,549
Oh, come on.

386
00:27:46,549 --> 00:27:51,114
It's not always simple to speak up.

387
00:28:01,961 --> 00:28:06,715
It's not always simple to wait either.

388
00:28:15,971 --> 00:28:17,816
Are you saying you used to wait...

389
00:28:17,816 --> 00:28:19,716
It's late.

390
00:28:19,716 --> 00:28:21,540
We should go home.

391
00:28:21,540 --> 00:28:24,148
We need to get up early tomorrow.

392
00:28:36,231 --> 00:28:38,958
As the Village Headman has urgent business to tend to,
[BAN KHUN OM HAET NOK SCHOOL SPORTS DAY]

393
00:28:38,958 --> 00:28:42,078
I'm here to commence the event on his behalf.

394
00:28:42,078 --> 00:28:47,295
The event wouldn't have happened without Khru Prince's creativity

395
00:28:47,295 --> 00:28:50,117
and the donation from me.

396
00:28:50,117 --> 00:28:53,774
Ever since the first day we met...

397
00:28:53,774 --> 00:28:58,601
Does he think this is the wedding of him and Khru Prince?

398
00:28:58,601 --> 00:29:00,868
Wow! Nice speech! So nice!

399
00:29:00,868 --> 00:29:04,266
The opening ceremony has ended. Give him a big hand, guys.

400
00:29:04,266 --> 00:29:05,339
Thank you.

401
00:29:05,339 --> 00:29:08,709
We're about to start the first game of the day.

402
00:29:08,709 --> 00:29:11,152
You're with me, the hottest MC.

403
00:29:11,152 --> 00:29:12,636
January, no!

404
00:29:12,636 --> 00:29:14,071
February, no!

405
00:29:14,071 --> 00:29:15,392
March, no!

406
00:29:15,392 --> 00:29:19,144
But it's April (Mesa)!

407
00:29:19,144 --> 00:29:21,623
And me, an MC who is hotter than mountain chillis.

408
00:29:21,623 --> 00:29:24,052
Yayah!

409
00:29:24,052 --> 00:29:25,465
Dr. Fah.

410
00:29:25,465 --> 00:29:28,117
Let's make today a fun day.

411
00:29:28,969 --> 00:29:31,627
The only fun thing I expect...

412
00:29:31,627 --> 00:29:34,823
is to see you buy everyone BBQ pork.

413
00:29:34,823 --> 00:29:36,455
Let's go, everyone.

414
00:29:36,455 --> 00:29:38,438
We're starting our first game here.

415
00:29:38,438 --> 00:29:39,947
This game is easy.

416
00:29:39,947 --> 00:29:44,171
Two people will be carrying the one on top.

417
00:29:44,171 --> 00:29:49,510
The one on top has a paper hat on and must steal the hat from the opponents.

418
00:29:49,510 --> 00:29:51,837
Ai Fah, why are you in a daze?

419
00:29:51,837 --> 00:29:53,349
Let's steal more hats.

420
00:29:53,349 --> 00:29:55,548
- Did we lose?
- Yes.

421
00:29:55,548 --> 00:29:58,010
Dr. Fah, why are you absent-minded?

422
00:29:58,010 --> 00:30:01,489
Wow! They're going all in. No one wants to lose here.

423
00:30:01,489 --> 00:30:03,998
Go! Go! Go!

424
00:30:03,998 --> 00:30:07,903
Viah, if we win, I'll buy you snacks for a whole month.

425
00:30:07,903 --> 00:30:11,030
- Really?
- Come on! One, two, three!

426
00:30:11,030 --> 00:30:13,400
Pull!

427
00:30:29,372 --> 00:30:31,072
Hey.

428
00:30:31,072 --> 00:30:32,729
If you've fallen, get back up.

429
00:30:32,729 --> 00:30:36,446
Or do you like sitting on me?

430
00:30:37,130 --> 00:30:39,183
