433
00:30:53,893 --> 00:30:57,193
It's time for me to step on your balloon now.

434
00:30:57,193 --> 00:30:58,570
No way.

435
00:30:58,570 --> 00:31:00,470
Are you sure?

436
00:31:01,470 --> 00:31:02,909
Where are you going?

437
00:31:02,909 --> 00:31:04,391
