438
00:31:04,391 --> 00:31:06,191
I'm sorry.

439
00:31:09,533 --> 00:31:11,969
So is this how you want it? Fine.

440
00:31:11,969 --> 00:31:14,530
Come on! Take that!

441
00:31:14,530 --> 00:31:16,390
Take this!

442
00:31:16,390 --> 00:31:18,790
There! Take that!

443
00:31:27,549 --> 00:31:29,149
Now what?

444
00:31:36,424 --> 00:31:38,999
Here's your food box.

445
00:31:39,854 --> 00:31:41,354
Thank you.

446
00:31:43,341 --> 00:31:44,911
I have a question.

447
00:31:44,911 --> 00:31:48,071
Why are you and Khru Prince fighting?

448
00:31:50,079 --> 00:31:51,779
It's nothing.

449
00:31:52,373 --> 00:31:54,963
I can tell even from the distance.

450
00:31:54,963 --> 00:31:58,488
Don't tell me you're fighting over me.

451
00:31:58,488 --> 00:32:00,943
I don't think so, Yayah.

452
00:32:00,943 --> 00:32:04,437
It's a long story.

453
00:32:04,437 --> 00:32:08,133
Go ahead and tell. I have time.

454
00:32:12,916 --> 00:32:15,274
So is that what happened?

455
00:32:16,241 --> 00:32:20,517
I actually understand you, Dr. Fah.

456
00:32:20,517 --> 00:32:22,105
Really?

457
00:32:23,121 --> 00:32:25,490
But I understand Khru Prince as well.

458
00:32:25,490 --> 00:32:28,509
I feel sorry for him.

459
00:32:28,509 --> 00:32:30,810
He's going through the same thing again.

460
00:32:30,810 --> 00:32:33,582
No wonder why he's so down.

461
00:32:34,623 --> 00:32:36,944
What do you mean, Yayah?

462
00:32:49,920 --> 00:32:54,923
We've come to the last sport of the day, which is a triathlon.

463
00:32:54,925 --> 00:32:59,004
That's right. It will be separated into three different types of sports.

464
00:32:59,004 --> 00:33:02,034
The first one is an eating challenge.

465
00:33:02,034 --> 00:33:05,337
The second sport is cycling.

466
00:33:05,337 --> 00:33:08,200
And the last one is

467
00:33:08,200 --> 00:33:12,100
