468
00:33:12,109 --> 00:33:14,248
Khru Prince, are you okay?

469
00:33:14,248 --> 00:33:16,151
I am fine, Sompor.

470
00:33:16,151 --> 00:33:17,441
I'm just warming up my leg.

471
00:33:17,441 --> 00:33:21,374
The triathlon sports will happen consecutively.

472
00:33:21,374 --> 00:33:24,959
The team that gets to the finish line first wins.

473
00:33:24,959 --> 00:33:26,905
If you're ready,

474
00:33:26,905 --> 00:33:32,509
three, two, one, go!

475
00:33:32,509 --> 00:33:35,751
