479
00:33:48,703 --> 00:33:53,743
The white team is tailing them so closely. So, so, so close.

480
00:34:03,441 --> 00:34:06,608
Come on. Faster.

481
00:34:08,954 --> 00:34:10,134
Tag my hand!

482
00:34:10,134 --> 00:34:11,822
Let's go.

483
00:34:11,822 --> 00:34:14,159
We've just started the second competition.

484
00:34:14,159 --> 00:34:17,106
What a close game.

485
00:34:17,106 --> 00:34:20,279
No way. The blue team is so much ahead.

486
00:34:20,279 --> 00:34:22,535
Can the white team catch up?

487
00:34:22,535 --> 00:34:26,215
Keep going. Keep cycling, my friend.

488
00:34:30,999 --> 00:34:32,117
It's your turn now, Khru Prince.

489
00:34:32,117 --> 00:34:36,614
- The white team has reached the three-legged race now.
- Let's go, Sompor.

490
00:34:37,721 --> 00:34:39,721
The blue team has just started.

491
00:34:39,721 --> 00:34:42,774
Will they catch up to the white team?

492
00:34:42,774 --> 00:34:46,436
Khru Prince has gone so far now.

493
00:34:46,436 --> 00:34:49,034
Khru Prince, are you all right?

494
00:34:51,301 --> 00:34:54,201
Ai Fah, come on!

495
00:34:54,201 --> 00:34:56,940
- Blue team!
- White team!

496
00:34:56,940 --> 00:35:01,430
- White team!
- Blue team!

497
00:35:04,076 --> 00:35:07,151
There's been a problem! What happened?

498
00:35:07,151 --> 00:35:08,701
Khru Prince just fell all of a sudden.

499
00:35:08,701 --> 00:35:12,200
Ai Fah, it's your chance now. Surpass him.

500
00:35:12,200 --> 00:35:14,088
Dr. Fah, why are you stopping?

501
00:35:14,088 --> 00:35:18,609
The blue team, keep going!

502
00:35:18,609 --> 00:35:21,100
Let's help Khru Prince up.

503
00:35:35,119 --> 00:35:38,175
Come on. Let's go to the finish line together.

504
00:35:42,378 --> 00:35:47,201
Wow! Dr. Fah comes back and helps Khru Prince up.

505
00:35:47,201 --> 00:35:52,460
What a lovely ship. No! I mean what an impressive race.

506
00:35:59,914 --> 00:36:03,480
And they finally get to the finish line together! Wow!

507
00:36:03,480 --> 00:36:05,400
Yes!

508
00:36:07,273 --> 00:36:12,060
The blue and white teams finished at the same time as a result of today's competition.

509
00:36:12,060 --> 00:36:14,310
We have a tie game.

510
00:36:14,310 --> 00:36:16,404
Yes!

511
00:36:16,404 --> 00:36:20,860
No matter who wins or loses,

512
00:36:20,860 --> 00:36:24,860
