513
00:36:31,914 --> 00:36:35,424
Khru Prince, is this the real gold?

514
00:36:35,424 --> 00:36:38,774
It's a chocolate medal. So delicious.

515
00:36:39,531 --> 00:36:42,421
That's only a consolation prize.

516
00:36:42,421 --> 00:36:48,687
What you best deserve is this one.

517
00:36:48,687 --> 00:36:50,397
You...

518
00:36:51,048 --> 00:36:53,054
How did you get it?

519
00:36:53,054 --> 00:36:58,637
Before the competition started, I went looking for it.

520
00:36:58,637 --> 00:37:02,178
Besides, I know about everything, Viah.

521
00:37:02,178 --> 00:37:03,513
Know what?

522
00:37:03,513 --> 00:37:05,660
About the fact that you

523
00:37:05,660 --> 00:37:10,360
