524
00:37:10,368 --> 00:37:15,148
But the one you gave Sompor was custom-made.

525
00:37:15,148 --> 00:37:16,797
That's right.

526
00:37:17,917 --> 00:37:22,364
I chose a pink hair clip because Sompor likes pink.

527
00:37:22,364 --> 00:37:26,915
Why didn't you tell Sompor from the beginning?

528
00:37:26,915 --> 00:37:29,012
Because it's not cool.

529
00:37:31,112 --> 00:37:36,658
But I think it's much cooler telling the truth.

530
00:37:36,658 --> 00:37:40,431
It's not too late to tell her.

531
00:37:40,431 --> 00:37:44,897
The sooner you tell, the sooner you'll look cool.

532
00:37:46,283 --> 00:37:47,506
Go on.

533
00:37:47,506 --> 00:37:49,217
Yes, sir.

534
00:37:58,088 --> 00:38:01,721
How is your ankle?

535
00:38:04,030 --> 00:38:05,909
I'm all right.

536
00:38:05,909 --> 00:38:07,305
Thank you.

537
00:38:07,305 --> 00:38:11,115
I think I'll take a look at it.

538
00:38:11,115 --> 00:38:12,515
Come on.

539
00:38:19,512 --> 00:38:23,617
[Medical Health Clinic]

540
00:38:27,389 --> 00:38:31,118
You got a sprained ankle. You should be fine.

541
00:38:31,118 --> 00:38:33,944
Next time, don't force it.

542
00:38:33,944 --> 00:38:39,424
No wonder you looked in pain when you were running.

543
00:38:39,424 --> 00:38:41,315
Thank you.

544
00:38:43,035 --> 00:38:44,504
You're welcome.

545
00:38:44,504 --> 00:38:48,427
It's a duty of a doctor to take care of his patients.

546
00:38:49,855 --> 00:38:54,802
I mean thank you for taking me to the finish line with you.

547
00:38:54,802 --> 00:38:58,065
And for finding the hair clip for Viah.

548
00:39:10,672 --> 00:39:12,572
- I'm sorry.
- I'm sorry.

549
00:39:15,054 --> 00:39:16,946
You speak first.

550
00:39:19,378 --> 00:39:22,870
I'm sorry for being unreasonable.

551
00:39:22,870 --> 00:39:27,117
There's no reason for me to be angry at you about that night.

552
00:39:29,500 --> 00:39:33,293
What if I say I understand?

553
00:39:34,045 --> 00:39:37,005
What do you mean?

554
00:39:37,005 --> 00:39:41,769
Yayah told me what you've been through.

555
00:39:41,769 --> 00:39:44,440
What do you mean, Yayah?

556
00:39:44,440 --> 00:39:50,174
Khru Prince told me he had a terrible ex.

557
00:39:50,983 --> 00:39:54,687
That person couldn't provide him with clarity.

558
00:39:54,687 --> 00:39:56,407
He came when he wanted to.

559
00:39:56,407 --> 00:39:58,285
He went with someone else when he felt like it.

560
00:39:58,285 --> 00:40:00,067
Khru Prince couldn't even get jealous.

561
00:40:00,067 --> 00:40:02,907
Because there was no established relationship.

562
00:40:02,907 --> 00:40:06,233
What did Khru Prince do?

563
00:40:06,233 --> 00:40:08,020
They were together for a brief period.

564
00:40:08,020 --> 00:40:12,180
Khru Prince couldn't endure it at last. He broke up with that person.

565
00:40:12,180 --> 00:40:17,447
And what you're doing is a repeat of what his ex did to him.

566
00:40:17,447 --> 00:40:20,154
No wonder why he's angry.

567
00:40:20,154 --> 00:40:23,460
He probably doesn't want to get hurt again.

568
00:40:26,814 --> 00:40:32,750
I wasn't being clear with you not because I'm not serious.

569
00:40:32,750 --> 00:40:40,470
But it's because I'm very serious that I'm afraid it's happening too soon.

570
00:40:40,470 --> 00:40:44,556
I'd been with my ex for seven years, yet we couldn't make it.

571
00:40:44,556 --> 00:40:48,244
That's why I don't want to rush things.

572
00:40:50,054 --> 00:40:53,254
But if my actions give you the wrong idea,

573
00:41:06,370 --> 00:41:09,237
from this moment on,

574
00:41:11,857 --> 00:41:14,097
may I pursue you?

575
00:41:24,572 --> 00:41:28,325
Prince, I'm returning the cap gun I borrowed.

576
00:41:30,343 --> 00:41:32,496
Am I interrupting?

577
00:41:32,496 --> 00:41:34,696
No.

578
00:41:34,696 --> 00:41:37,643
Will you please excuse me?

579
00:41:43,632 --> 00:41:45,232
Thank you.

580
00:41:54,057 --> 00:41:56,237
What were you two talking about?

581
00:41:57,500 --> 00:41:59,441
What was it?

582
00:41:59,441 --> 00:42:03,720
It's nothing. I was just giving him first aid.

583
00:42:21,403 --> 00:42:23,509
Where are you going?

584
00:42:26,266 --> 00:42:30,050
That gunshot was a signal to start.

585
00:42:30,050 --> 00:42:34,540
This game isn't going to be as easy as the one we competed in today.

586
00:42:34,540 --> 00:42:36,611
We'll see about that.

587
00:42:36,611 --> 00:42:41,144
Because I've never lost to anyone.

588
00:42:59,187 --> 00:43:02,090
I just want to try hard.

589
00:43:02,090 --> 00:43:06,154
I want to stop everything just to be with him.

590
00:43:10,669 --> 00:43:12,472
Hey! What are you doing?

591
00:43:12,472 --> 00:43:14,395
You allowed me to pursue you.

592
00:43:14,395 --> 00:43:18,151
From now on, I'll just pursue you non-stop.

593
00:43:18,151 --> 00:43:20,140
Prepare yourself for that.

594
00:43:20,140 --> 00:43:23,550
Can I put my hand right here until it gets warmer?

595
00:43:23,550 --> 00:43:25,092
Prince, this way.

596
00:43:25,092 --> 00:43:27,499
Khru Prince already has someone he's talking to.

597
00:43:27,499 --> 00:43:30,176
Don't worry. I'm not trying to steal him.

598
00:43:30,176 --> 00:43:34,095
I just want him to meet someone who can take care of him better than me.

599
00:43:34,095 --> 00:43:36,551
- What are you doing?
- Your friend should know

600
00:43:36,551 --> 00:43:40,060
you have a doctor to take care of you up on the mountain.

601
00:43:40,060 --> 00:43:44,910
♫ Do you believe that there is still hope for your love? ♫

602
00:43:44,910 --> 00:43:47,880
♫ Even in your dreams every night ♫

603
00:43:47,880 --> 00:43:53,070
♫ Love is still waiting for you to come and change your dreams ♫

604
00:43:53,070 --> 00:43:56,770
♫ So they can turn into reality ♫

605
00:43:56,770 --> 00:44:00,940
♫ If you're the sea, I'll be like the sand ♫

606
00:44:00,940 --> 00:44:07,120
♫ If you're the sky, please let me be ♫

607
00:44:07,120 --> 00:44:11,380
♫ The North to guide your heart ♫

608
00:44:11,380 --> 00:44:17,490
♫ To be next to mine, like the sky and starlight ♫
